Name: The Incredible Adventures of Van Helsing

Achievements.Name: Coil Collector
Achievements.Description: Complete the Start the Generator quest.

Achievements.Name: Manservant
Achievements.Description: Gain entrance to the village of Markovna with the help of Lady Katarina.

Achievements.Name: Chicken Runner
Achievements.Description: Kill a chicken with a sword!

Achievements.Name: Let loose the ghost of war
Achievements.Description: Let Lady Katarina kill a Boss.

Achievements.Name: Escort Master
Achievements.Description: Escort the Traveling Merchant to the Romany Camp with him taking no damage.

Achievements.Name: Viva la Resistance!
Achievements.Description: Solve every side-quest in the Helsing lair.

Achievements.Name: Spotless Defense
Achievements.Description: Defend the Lair without a single enemy getting in.

Achievements.Name: Explosives expert
Achievements.Description: Finsh the Slavage Mission quest without setting of any explosives.

Achievements.Name: Riddle me Wisp
Achievements.Description: Answer all the Riddle Wisps correctly (so you don't have to fight them).

Achievements.Name: What's in the bag?
Achievements.Description: Take 20 pieces of loot from the Domovoy on the Gorgon Pass.

Achievements.Name: I'm so Hardcore!
Achievements.Description: Finish the game with a Hardcore character!
